content:
Cryptocurrency exchange Bitfinex has tightened its know-your-customer (KYC) process, The Block has learned.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
According to an email sent to Bitfinex’s verified users, seen by The Block, the exchange is enhancing its due-diligence procedures in an effort to bring all of its client accounts “to the same level.”&nbsp;
